name: Master Luke
Lore: 'Until being reunited with Yoda, Luke suspected that he had completed his training. Has a strong influence on the weak minded.',
Text: 'Deploys -2 on Tatooine. Power -2 when present with Vader. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When in battle, may target one opponent''s alien present. Draw destiny. Target returns to opponent''s hand if destiny > ability. Immune to attrition < 4.',
